  section.section
    h2.header_3 Context
    
  section.section
    p.par SoloTouch is my second project under LUME, a research program aimed at creating musical interfaces for individuals with special needs. In this project, I partnered with Mubarak Marafa to design an instrument for those who lack access to formal musical training.
    
  section.section
    div.diagram
