  section.section
    h2.header_2 Reflections and Learnings
  
  section.section
    p.par SoloTouch was one of my first design projects. It was truly an encouragement to achieve such success from an early attempt in design, one that allowed me to set a high bar for future projects. Looking back at the design, I would definitely improve upon the learnability of our system, perhaps even removing the iPhone controller altogether for further simplicity.
    
  section.section
    p.par I am glad to have gotten our hands on an actual 3D-printed model during the design process, as it enabled us to uncover issues that would not have otherwise been found, leading to the iterative designs that made the final product so much better.
    
